CREATE STREAM PAGEVIEWS_FEMALE_LIKE_89 WITH (KAFKA_TOPIC='pageviews_enriched_r8_r9', PARTITIONS=1, REPLICAS=1, VALUE_FORMAT='AVRO') AS SELECT *
FROM PAGEVIEWS_FEMALE PAGEVIEWS_FEMALE
WHERE ((PAGEVIEWS_FEMALE.REGIONID LIKE '%_8') OR (PAGEVIEWS_FEMALE.REGIONID LIKE '%_9'))
EMIT CHANGES;
